CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, February 9, 1963, pg. 4, reads: "The Star! - Alberta Thompson was the star of the D.I. style show last Sunday night at Holiday House. The benefit show and dance aided the MENDS fund. - Harris Photo"
TitMainTitle: Portrait of Alberta Thompson wearing dark pants, fur trimmed boots, and dark textured sweater with hood with light colored flecking, standing in Holiday House for annual D. I. Club MENDS benefit
